//app.gopostmatic.com">upgrading</a>.</p>\n<h3>Have a free trial. On us.</h3>\n<p>We&#8217;re making Postmatic Premium free for 14 days during our launch. We&#8217;ve worked hard to create the best engagement platform for WordPress and think you&#8217;ll love it. <a href="http://app.gopostmatic.com/">Get started on your free two week trial today</a>.<br />\n<img class="size-full wp-image-600" src="http://gopostmatic.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/team1.png" alt="team" width="400" /></p>\n<p>PS &#8211; Your reviews mean a lot to us. When you have a second head over to wordpress.org and <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/postmatic" target="_blank">let us know your thoughts</a>?</p>\n</div>\n<h1>Take engagement to the next level with <strong>Postmatic Premium</strong></h1>\n<h4 style="margin-top: 35px;">Give your readers something pretty to look at and easy to use. Postmatic Premium lets you deliver <strong>beautiful and responsive html emails</strong>, with <strong>enhanced email commenting</strong>.</h4>\n<h4>Plus, you’ll enjoy the simplicity of <strong>100% email-based comment moderation</strong> and have your content looking its best in a <strong>customizable template</strong>. You’ll also benefit from <strong>the best email delivery rates in the industry</strong>.</h4>\n<p><a class="button button-primary button-large" href="http://gopostmatic.com/premium">Learn about Postmatic Premium</a></p>\n<h2>Perfect html emails that look beautiful on desktop, tablet or mobile.</h2>\n<p>You do your thing and post like you normally do. We’ll make sure everything looks perfect with support for images, galleries, oEmbeds and more.</p>\n<h2>A fully responsive template – regardless of what you put in it.</h2>\n<p>We take the work out of displaying your post as a beautiful email, regardless of the device.<br />\nPostmatic uses a customizable template for sending posts to your subscribers. Your content is presented in a simple, elegant manner on any device—all while taking advantage of client-specific functionality.</p>\n<h2>Complex conversations become as easy as email.</h2>\n<p>Not only does Postmatic Premium put your newly published posts in to rich html templates, but it does the same for comment notifications as well.</p>\n<p>Like magic, we bring the comment stream directly to your reader’s inbox with support for gravatars, post recaps and intelligent threaded commenting context. Comments get delivered in a way that makes the whole picture clearer. Which gives your reader more understanding and creates much better conversations.</p>\n<h2>Outgoing mail delivery using Mailchimp and Rackspace</h2>\n<p>Regardless of your web host and their ideas about email throttling, you can be sure posts and comments will get to where they’re going, as quickly as possible. We use the same infrastructure as Mailchimp and Rackspace to send with the highest deliverability rates in the industry. Fifty thousand subscribers? No problem.</p>\n<h2>Moderate new comments by email</h2>\n<p>WordPress notifications are, well, just notifications. We can do better than that. Postmatic Premium lets you moderate comments by email with a simple word. Just reply with <em>approve</em>, <em>trash</em> or <em>spam </em>and we’ll take care of the rest.</p>\n<h2 id="trial" class="clear"><a href="http://gopostmatic.com/trial">➜ Try it for free for two weeks and send your engagement through the roof. On us.</a></h2>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"https://gopostmatic.com/update/welcome-message-for-free-users/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lan