button-large" href="http://gopostmatic.com/premium">Learn about Postmatic Premium</a></p>\n<div class="col">\n<h4><strong>Embed all the media you’d like</strong></h4>\n<p>Postmatic Premium templates support images, galleries and oEmbeds from all the major audio and video services like Soundcloud, Vimeo and YouTube. Automatically.</p>\n<p>We’ll even embed documents from Issuu and display good-looking invites from Meetup.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col">\n<h4><strong>Plays well with others</strong></h4>\n<p>Content from your favorite WordPress plugins or shortcodes will automatically be rendered as email-friendly html when you publish your posts. Automatically.</p>\n<p>Insert whatever you want, like recipes, tables, galleries, videos, invitations or as. We’ll make sure it<br />\nlooks great.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col" style="margin-bottom: 45px;">\n<h4><strong>Automatic content optimization</strong></h4>\n<p>Our magic template knows what’s good for desktop and what can render on mobile. We’ll adjust the formatting on your content accordingly.</p>\n<p>We’ll even use reverse- markdown to create the best looking text-only version for folks using simple email clients, older phones or those in remote areas.</p>\n</div>\n<h4 style="clear: both;">Give your readers something pretty to look at and easy to use. Postmatic Premium lets you<br />\ndeliver <strong>beautiful and responsive html emails</strong>, with <strong>enhanced email commenting</strong>.</h4>\n<h4>Plus, you’ll enjoy the simplicity of <strong>100% email-based comment moderation</strong> and have your content<br />\nlooking its best in a <strong>customizable template</strong>. You’ll also benefit from <strong>the best email<br />\ndelivery rates in the industry</strong>.</h4>\n<p>It’s all in Postmatic Premium.</p>\n<h2 id="trial" class="clear"><a href="http://gopostmatic.com/trial">➜ Try it for free for two weeks and send your engagement through the roof. On us.</a></h2>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_b