(4, 1, '2015-11-08 04:10:23', '2015-11-08 04:10:23', '<div class="main homePage">\r\n<section class="secOne">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<div class="central">\r\n<h1>Individualized How-to Guides to help exceptional family members thrive</h1><img alt="Paula" class="homeLargeImage mariaImage" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula.png" />\r\n<h1 class="meetMaria">Meet Paula</h1>\r\n<h2>Paula has a 13-year-old with special needs. Worrying about his future keeps her up at night. Information online is overwhelming, unreliable and generic. Expert help is too expensive.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<aside>\r\n<h3>Our Free Guides</h3>\r\n<p>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds) and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=303">Create an effective IEP</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=268">Optimize health insurance</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=357">Apply for SSI</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=184">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class="donate">Donate</h3>\r\n<p>Each Exceptional Lives Guide takes many hours to research, publish and update. Keep them free (and ad-free) for everyone by making a donation today.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://www.givingcommon.org/profile/1142565/exceptional-lives-inc/#8">Donate</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<img alt="Guidestar Logo" class="guidestarSilver" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/guidestarSilver.png" />\r\n</aside>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="secTwo">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<img alt="Laptop Screenshot" class="homeLargeImage laptop" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/laptop.png" />\r\n<h2>When she visits the Exceptional Lives website, she finds free, easy-to-understand online guides for families of children and adults with disabilities in Massachusetts.</h2>\r\n<h1>Each guide takes as little as 15 minutes to walk through!</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="secThree">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<img alt="Guides Screenshot 1" class="squareImg" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/screenshot1.png" />\r\n<h2>As Paula moves through a Guide, she answers questions. The software behind the Guides uses these answers to customize the information she sees.</h2><img alt="Guides Screenshot 2" class="squareImg" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/screenshot2.png" />\r\n<h2>Each Guide gives her clear next steps that empower her to take action and achieve goals.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="secFour">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<img alt="Paula 2" class="homeLargeImage cartoon" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula2.png" />\r\n<h2>By using Exceptional Lives Guides, Paula has more knowledge and confidence about how to access the necessary supports and services that will help her son thrive.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="secFive">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<div class="central">\r\n<h1>Ready to get started?</h1>\r\n<h2>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds), and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=303">Create an effective IEP</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=268">Optimize health insurance</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=357">Apply for SSI</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=184">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<aside>\r\n<h3>Subscribe to our blog:</h3>\r\n[sola_nl_sign_up]\r\n<p class="clear"></p>\r\n<p class="noSpam">We do not spam. Read our <a href="http://exceptionallives.org/TermsOfService">privacy policy</a></p>\r\n<h3>Follow us on social media:</h3>\r\n<div class="socialIconsWrap">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/exceptional.lives" target="_blank"><i class="facebookIcon"></i></a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="https://twitter.com/xceptionallives" target="_blank"><i class="twitterIcon"></i></a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/10226036" target="_blank"><i class="linkedinIcon"></i></a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<a href="https://instagram.com/exceptional.lives/"><i class="instagramIcon"></i></a>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</aside>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<p class="copyright">&copy; Copyright Exceptional Lives. All rights reserved.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2015-11-10 10:01:36', '2015-11-10 10:01:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=4', 0, 'page', '', 0),
