(28, 1, '2015-11-10 09:04:57', '2015-11-10 09:04:57', '<div class="main homePage">\n    <section class="secOne">\n        <div id="widthWrapper">\n            <div class="central">\n                <h1>Individualized How-to Guides to help exceptional family members thrive</h1><img alt="Paula" class="homeLargeImage mariaImage" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula.png" />\n                <h1 class="meetMaria">Meet Paula</h1>\n                <h2>Paula has a 13-year-old with special needs. Worrying about his future keeps her up at night. Information online is overwhelming, unreliable and generic. Expert help is too expensive.</h2>\n            </div>\n            <aside>\n                <h3>Our Free Guides</h3>\n                <p>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds) and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=303">Create an effective IEP</a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=268">Optimize health insurance</a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=357">Apply for SSI</a>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=184">Navigate guardianship</a>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n                <h3 class="donate">Donate</h3>\n                <p>Each Exceptional Lives Guide takes many hours to research, publish and update. Keep them free (and ad-free) for everyone by making a donation today.</p>\n                <p>\n                    <a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://www.g