(93, 1, '2015-11-09 03:15:10', '2015-11-09 03:15:10', '<div class="main homePage"><section class="secOne">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<div class="central">\r\n<h1>Individualized How-to Guides to help exceptional family members thrive</h1>\r\n<img class="homeLargeImage mariaImage" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula.png" alt="Paula" />\r\n<h1 class="meetMaria">Meet Paula</h1>\r\n<h2>Paula is a 13-year-old with special needs. Worrying about her future keeps her up at night. Information online is overwhelming, unreliable and generic. Expert help is too expensive.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<aside>\r\n<h3>Our Free Guides</h3>\r\nClick a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds) and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="#">Create an effective IEP</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Optimize health insurance</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Apply for SSI</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n<h3 class="donate">Donate</h3>\r\nEach Exceptional Lives Guide takes many hours to research, publish and update. Keep them free (and ad-free) for everyone by making a donation today.\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="#">Donate</a><img class="guidestarSilver" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/guidestarSilver.png" alt="Guidestar Logo" />\r\n\r\n</aside></div>\r\n</section><section class="secTwo">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="homeLargeImage laptop" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/laptop.png" alt="Laptop Screenshot" />\r\n<h2>When she visits the Exceptional Lives website, she finds free, easy-to-understand online guides for families of children and adults with disabilities in Massachusetts.</h2>\r\n<h1>Each guide takes as little as 15 minutes to walk through!</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class="secThree">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="squareImg" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/screenshot1.png" alt="Guides Screenshot 1" />\r\n<h2>As Paula moves through a Guide, she answers questions. The software behind the Guides uses these answers to customize the information she sees.</h2>\r\n<img class="squareImg" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/screenshot2.png" alt="Guides Screenshot 2" />\r\n<h2>Each Guide gives her clear next steps that empower her to take action and achieve goals.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class="secFour">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="homeLargeImage cartoon" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula2.png" alt="Paula 2" />\r\n<h2>By using Exceptional Lives Guides, Paula has more knowledge and confidence about how to access the necessary supports and services that will help her son thrive.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class="secFive">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<div class="central">\r\n<h1>Ready to get started?</h1>\r\n<h2>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds), and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</h2>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Create an effective IEP</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Optimize health insurance</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Apply for SSI</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<aside>\r\n<h3>Subscribe to our blog:</h3>\r\n<form><input type="email" name="sub_email" required="" placeholder="Email Address">\r\n<div class="asideFormRow"><label>We do not spam. Read our <a href="#">privacy policy</a></label><input type="submit" class="subscribe button"  value="Subscribe"></div>\r\n\r\n<div style="display:none">\r\n   <input name="action" value="sola_nl_sign_up_add_sub" type="hidden">\r\n   <input name="security" value="2e412d8992" type="hidden"></div><div>\r\n</div>\r\n</form>\r\n<h3>Follow us on social media:</h3>\r\n<div class="socialIconsWrap"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/exceptional.lives" target="_blank"><i class="facebookIcon"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/xceptionallives" target="_blank"><i class="twitterIcon"></i></a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/10226036" target="_blank"><i class="linkedinIcon"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="instagramIcon"></i></a></div>\r\n</aside></div>\r\n</section>\r\n<p class="copyright">© Copyright Exceptional Lives. All rights reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-09 03:15:10', '2015-11-09 03:15:10', '', 4, 'http://localhost:8888/2015/11/09/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
