(118, 1, '2015-11-10 00:46:59', '2015-11-10 00:46:59', '<div class="main homePage"><section class="secOne">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<div class="central">\r\n<h1>Individualized How-to Guides to help exceptional family members thrive</h1>\r\n<img class="homeLargeImage mariaImage" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula.png" alt="Paula" />\r\n<h1 class="meetMaria">Meet Paula</h1>\r\n<h2>Paula has a 13-year-old with special needs. Worrying about his future keeps her up at night. Information online is overwhelming, unreliable and generic. Expert help is too expensive.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<aside>\r\n<h3>Our Free Guides</h3>\r\n<p>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds) and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</p>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=303">Create an effective IEP</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=268">Optimize health insurance</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=357">Apply for SSI</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=184">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n<h3 class="donate">Donate</h3>\r\n<p>Each Exceptional Lives Guide takes many hours to research, publish and update. Keep them free (and ad-free) for everyone by making a donation today.</p>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://www.givingcommon.org/profile/1142565/exceptional-lives-inc/#8">Donate</a><img class="guidestarSilver" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/guidestarSilver.png" alt="Guidestar Logo" />\r\n\r\n</aside></div>\r\n</section><section class="secTwo">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="homeLargeImage laptop" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/laptop.png" alt="Laptop Screenshot" />\r\n<h2>When she visits the Exceptional Lives website, she finds free, easy-to-understand online guides for families of children and adults with disabilities in Massachusetts.</h2>\r\n<h1>Each guide takes as little as 15 minutes to walk through!</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class="secThree">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="squareImg" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/screenshot1.png" alt="Guides Screenshot 1" />\r\n<h2>As Paula moves through a Guide, she answers questions. The software behind the Guides uses these answers to customize the information she sees.</h2>\r\n<img class="squareImg" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/screenshot2.png" alt="Guides Screenshot 2" />\r\n<h2>Each Guide gives her clear next steps that empower her to take action and achieve goals.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class="secFour">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="homeLargeImage cartoon" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/paula2.png" alt="Paula 2" />\r\n<h2>By using Exceptional Lives Guides, Paula has more knowledge and confidence about how to access the necessary supports and services that will help her son thrive.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class="secFive">\r\n<div id="widthWrapper">\r\n<div class="central">\r\n<h1>Ready to get started?</h1>\r\n<h2>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds), and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</h2>\r\n<a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Create an effective IEP</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Optimize health insurance</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Apply for SSI</a><a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="#">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<aside>\r\n<h3>Subscribe to our blog:</h3>\r\n[sola_nl_sign_up]\r\n<p>We do not spam. Read our <a href="http://exceptionallives.org/TermsOfService">privacy policy</a></p>\r\n<h3>Follow us on social media:</h3>\r\n<div class="socialIconsWrap"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/exceptional.lives" target="_blank"><i class="facebookIcon"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/xceptionallives" target="_bla