                <h2>Click a button below to check out an Exceptional Lives Guide! Create your own account (takes 15 seconds), and explore all our Guides. It''s that easy.</h2>\r\n                <ul>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing firstBut" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=303">Create an effective IEP</a>\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=268">Optimize health insurance</a>\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=357">Apply for SSI</a>\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        <a class="button buttonStackSpacing" href="https://navitomeapp.com/?pid=184">Navigate guardianship</a>\r\n                    </li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <aside>\r\n                <h3>Subscribe to our blog:</h3>\r\n                [sola_nl_sign_up]\r\n                <p class="clear"></p>\r\n                <p class="noSpam">We do not spam. Read our <a href="http://exceptionallives.org/TermsOfService">privacy policy</a></p>\r\n                <h3>Follow us on social media:</h3>\r\n                <div class="socialIconsWrap">\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>\r\n                            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/exceptional.lives" target="_blank"><i class="facebookIcon"></i></a>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li>\r\n                            <a href="https://twitter.com/xceptionallives" target="_blank"><i class="twitterIcon"></i></a>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li>\r\n                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/10226036" target="_blank"><i class="linkedinIcon"></i></a>\r\n                     